  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - Age 65 or older Patient does not have the capacity to make decisions Patient admitted to
        the ICU with life threatening illness including advanced heart, renal, lung,
        gastrointestinal and oncologic disease Patient has English speaking representative to make
        decisions on his/her behalf Patient critically ill and unlikely to survive to hospital
        discharge

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - Patients who are imminently dying and admitted to the ICU are excluded Wards if the state
      </textblock>
